le":"Thief of Hearts","video":false,"overview":"A woman trapped in a boring marriage begins an affair with a handsome man who seems able to read her mind. She doesn't know that he has broken into her house and read her diaries, where she has recorded her deepest thoughts and fantasies.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":0.6662,"vote_count":43,"poster_path":"/be08f4q9Doq5HvHgBCS5NzQ6jja.jpg","release_date":"1984-10-19","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/amvcq28G3gPqZxkqoa6Q62j1Ma8.jpg","original_title":"Thief of Hearts","original_language":"en"},{"id":48485,"adult":false,"title":"Nostradamus","video":false,"overview":"A dramatic retelling of the life of Michel de Nostredame, from his early work as a plague doctor to his time at the court of Catherine de Medici, after he became famed for his prophetic almanacs. Stars Rutger Hauer and Julia Ormond.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.4822,"vote_count":74,"poster_path":"/kbjPR7FoKUUv4uR4dwzO7ce4aTx.jpg","release_date":"1994-08-18","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/pTlT8oJnNiJUlgwxijhJMdACC7i.jpg","original_title":"Nostradamus","original_language":"en"},{"id":313080,"adult":false,"title":"The Ponzi Scheme","video":false,"overview":"Ponzi, from his arrival in Boston in 1903, to hi death in Rio in 1949. He made himself famous in inventing the first fraud of modern times on a large scale, and inspired Bernard Madoff.","genre_ids":[36,18],"popularity":0.249,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/d6QrglHhOknYkwXjfGXUhonN3Oz.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-14","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/n1DfrIwuSzs8jyzMPzRQeYAh5a8.jpg","original_title":"Le système de Ponzi","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1109402,"adult":false,"title":"Her Body","video":false,"overview":"A Czech high diver's Olympic dreams are shattered when she suffers a devastating injury while training. Forced to leave the sport she loves, she follows a photographer friend into the world of nude modeling, ultimately reinventing herself as an adult film actress. Inspired by the true story of diving champion Andrea Absolonová.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.6021,"vote_count":39,"poster_path":"/foNYeBzrTpz94Sg9yV6hGMsax8A.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-16","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/ffOxfVhSMcHiM26kWFQ9Lto4v6s.jpg","original_title":"Její tělo","original_language":"cs"},{"id":48750,"adult":false,"title":"Les Miserables","video":false,"overview":"In WWII France, poor and illiterate Henri Fortin is introduced to Victor Hugo's classic novel Les Misérables and begins to see parallels between the book and his own life.","genre_ids":[18,36],"popularity":0.4937,"vote_count":84,"poster_path":"/toQ6BJCiKVSnklpsma2GnJ6KKah.jpg","release_date":"1995-03-22","vote_average":6.649,"backdrop_path":"/elJMAU9XXxk02KmZ7zlQtFlBq0J.jpg","original_title":"Les Misérables","original_language":"fr"},{"id":1109484,"adult":false,"title":"Half-Light","video":false,"overview":"A couple debates having unprotected car sex late at night.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.4504,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/q4OOs9XY8wjEdGR88gHDV712D9Q.jpg","release_date":"2023-04-30","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Half-Light","original_language":"en"},{"id":49022,"adult":false,"title":"Something Borrowed","video":false,"overview":"Though Rachel is a successful attorney and a loyal, generous friend, she is still single. After one drink too many at her 30th-birthday celebration, Rachel unexpectedly falls into bed with her longtime crush, Dex -- who happens to be engaged to her best friend, Darcy. Ramifications of the liaison threaten to destroy the women's lifelong friendship, while Ethan, Rachel's confidant, harbors a potentially explosive secret of his own.","genre_ids":[35,18,10749],"popularity":1.9746,"vote_count":1078,"poster_path":"/66VZu75VeLGc6tcAypqyGzWcPeN.jpg","release_date":"2011-05-05","vote_average":6.237,"backdrop_path":"/pKh2qMYoC5vXaRiU0qBK3IPXk76.jpg","original_title":"Something Borrowed","original_language":"en"},{"id":705991,"adult"